translation[11]{c,v,t}:
  10,43,"Ukanti phakathi kwabo kukho abaye bakujonge (ndla ngamehlo), kodwa ungaze ukwazi ukukhokela iimfama na nokuba aziboni"
  10,44,"Inene uAllâh Akaboni abantu nangantoni na, koko ngabantu ngokwabo abazonayo"
  10,45,"NgeMini Aza kubahlanganisela ndawonye bonke, iya kuba ngathi azanga bakhe bahlale (kweli hlabathi) iya kuba ngathi baphile iyure enye yemini. Baya kwazana. Abaya kutshabalala ngokwenyani ngabo babephika indibano yabo noAllâh, bengengabo nabakhokelelekileyo"
  10,46,"Enokuba Singakubonisa na (ngoku usaphilayo Muhammad) okuthile koko Sibathembise ngako (kusisohlwayo), okanye Sikwenze ufe (ungakubonanga), kuya kuhlala kukuThi apho baza kubuyela khona, ngapha koko uAllâh UliNgqina loko bakwenzayo"
  10,47,"Isizwe ngasinye sinoMthunywa (waso), uya kuthi akufika umthunywa (lowo esizweni sakhe) umcimbi ugwetywe phakathi kwabo ngobulungisa, yaye abazi koniwa"
  10,48,"Ke kaloku bathi: “Siya kufika nini na esi sithembiso (sesohlwayo), ukuba ngaba nithetha inyaniso?”"
  10,49,"Yithi (Muhammad): “Mna andinamandla akwenza bubi esiqwini sam, kungekho nzuzo ndinokuzizuzisa yona ngaphandle koko uAllâh Athande (ukundenza kona).” Sizwe ngasinye sinexesha esilibekelweyo, lisakufika ixesha (elo) labo abangekhe balilibazise bengekhe balikhawulezise nangeyure (enye)"
  10,50,"Yithi: “Khanindixeleleni ke, ukuba isohlwayo eso saKhe sinokunihlela ngobusuku okanye emini, yiyiphi inxalenye yaso abenzi bobubi abanokuyingxamela.”"
  10,51,"Makube ke ngoko niya kuthi xa sithe sehla ngokwenene, nikholwe kuso? (kuze kuthiwe kuni): “Nithini na ke ngoku? Kudala kakade nisingxamele!”"
  10,52,"Kekalokukuyakuthiwakuboabobazonayoimiphefumloyabo: “Ngcamlani ke isohlwayo sanaphakade? Ingaba nibuyekezwe ngakumbi na ngaphandle koko nakusebenzelayo?”"
  10,53,"Bayakucela (Muhammad) ukuba ubaxelele ukuba: “Ingaba iyinyani na (into yokuba isohlwayo neMini yokuGqibela siza kwenzeka)?” Yithi: “Ewe! Ndifunga ngeNkosi yam! Iyinyani ngokwenene yaye anisayi kuphuncula kuzo!”"